        Dad :-</font><br>
        <b><font color="#663366" face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="+1">&nbsp; </font><font size="+2">Dr.
        P. P. Vaidya</font></font></b><br>
        <font size="+1" color="#663366" face="Comic Sans MS">M</font><font color="#000000"><font size="+1" face="Comic Sans MS">y
        dad is a renowned senior practioner working in Sanjeevan Hospital, <a href="http://www.himachalonline.com/mandi/index.htm">Mandi</a>,
        <a href="http://www.himachalonline.com/">H.P.</a>, India and is a leading surgeon in whole of Himachal Pradesh
        State. He did his M.B.B.S from Srinagar medical college and his M.S.
        from Banarus Hindu University (BHU), Varanasi, U.P., India. He worked in
        government service for around 20 years and then joined Sanjeevan
        Hospital.</font><br>
        <font size="+1" face="Comic Sans MS">My Dad has a very strong
        personality and I have learnt many good things from him. He has been
        guiding me constantly in the right way and also helps me out in any
        difficulty which I face. He has gained much respect in this small town
        and almost all people know him and respect him. I am proud to have him
        as my Dad.</font></font></p>
        <!--msthemeseparator--><p align="center"><img src="images/anarule.gif"></p>
        <p align="justify"><font size="+1" color="#ff0000" face="Comic Sans MS">My
        Mom :-</font><br>
        <font color="#663366" face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="+1">&nbsp; </font><b><font size="+2">Dr.
        Raj Vaidya</font></b></font><br>
        <font size="+1" face="Comic Sans MS" color="#000000">My mom is a
        renowned gynecologist and anesthetist and is running her own clinic (RAJ
        CLINIC) in Mandi and is also on call from Sanjeevan Hospital. She did
        her M.B.B.S from Lady Harding Medical College, Delhi. She was also a
        government servant before she took courage and opened up her own clinic.
        My Mom is very brave person and no hardships can stop her from doing
        what she thinks is right. She has a memory of around One Million Gigabytes
        and can also handle multiple processes at the same time. She has been
        and is still my idol. She has taught me how to face this harsh world and
        also how to deal with people. What I am right now is majorly due to her
        and my dad. They have been my constant source of inspiration. I really
        thank GOD to give me such a wonderful mother.</font></p>
