        sweetheart, is currently pursuing her M.B.A. from <a href="http://www.ppc.edu">Point
        Park University (PPU)</a>, <a href="http://www.city.pittsburgh.pa.us/">Pittsburgh</a>,
        <a href="http://www.state.pa.us">PA</a>, USA. Born and brought up in Mandi, Himachal Pradesh, India; she did
        her initial schooling from Mandi and completed her B.B.A (Bachelor in
        Business Administration) and M.B.A. from Himachal Pradesh University,
        Simla, India. She was the topper of her batch in MBA program. She worked
        for around three years in &quot;<a href="http://www.theassociates.com">The Associates</a>&quot;, a Citigroup
        company as an Assistant&nbsp;Manager, Consumer Business before coming to PPU for her MBA. I
        love her very much.</font></p>
